{"type": "article", "id": 49826, "title": "Gucci 推出狗年表情， OPPO R11s 日本上市广告语不变 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-02-01T04:29:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47503, "name": "农历狗年"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 23315, "name": "野兽派"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180201120638hl96Iqo03Pjg8aWH.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25590.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Timberland 和手游《光荣使命》合作</b></a>，在游戏中推出一组“军事+时尚”主题新战士形象。可以看到他们都穿了 Timberland 的鞋。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201120114j8NbIJLMXvchD4Fp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.410937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5Mjc0MTc5Nw==&amp;mid=2247499117&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4381738f1ac581cf288b3c960faf2580&amp;chksm=ec7e0aa7db0983b14860243aa313765e76e5883f04efd22c2ab38dafc337c57096b30d0ed029&amp;scene=0&amp;key=bfc1c7babd5d6b591f4a4f93785cc340790481f14a3980723dc9474147224cbeab76b34384fcff1bceaa943efd61ec012c32b34b4091370a310b4b9319edc521a3efce1544f61f5cf2526f8a5abbf23d&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=eCzM7%2BvRVTmer0yU7uQ9fo0dywYff9d4NdGTDxnN106KHfnS8a9I11jKHUkzL1n0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>野兽派在上海新天地开了一家叫作 Little B 的概念店</b></a>，可以找到水、小零食、牙膏、化妆品等，当然还有花。这个不锈钢打造的铁皮房，共分为：外带饮品区、艺术展览区和精品超市区 3 个部分。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201114520Fq3QvsygOel9YXhH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745505\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201114555iRp3D60TVnMbSujr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746556\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201114605F2kjyhzBPLgHREJY.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767956\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-43358.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>OPPO 在日本市场召开新品发布会</b></a>，正式发布 OPPO R11s，而该款手机也是 OPPO 在日本推出的第一款产品，广告语是日文版的“充电五分钟，通话两小时”……</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201111505Y4qeSCA8aL6ouOMz.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659030\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/case-of-jingdong-nianhuojie-20180131\" rel=\"nofollow\">京东发布年货节《温情三部曲》广告：《小城之念》、《山间之望》、《双城之盼》。</a></b><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201115630n4aTJSwuL2Mjf1bA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.595973\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 22.5px; font: 15.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 22.5px; font: 15.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 23.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 20.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #f8a901; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 20.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #f8a901; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 21.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 20.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #f8a901; -webkit-text-stroke: #ffffff} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #ffffff; min-height: 22.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 20.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #f8a901} span.s3 {font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 20.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #f8a901; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25658.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gucci 为迎接农历狗年，专门开发了一款Animoji 表情</b></a>，还挺可爱。狗的灵感来自于 GUCCI 创意总监 Alessandro Michele 自己的波士顿猎犬 Bosco 和 Orso，并由御用画师 Unskilled Worker 绘画。猎犬从耳朵到嘴都能动，项圈吊牌有明显的 “GUCCI” 标志。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180201115750PsV3q0YENg2cOX1e.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p><a href=\"http://lanxiongsports.com/?c=posts&amp;a=view&amp;id=9238\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>加拿大运动品牌 lululemon 推出了以中国春节为主题的品牌概念</b></a>。以十个具有中国传统文化意义的代表为灵感，打造十项适于生活中每个时刻的练习形式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802011202268ThmXZIrP7zHt9gx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.413846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-3-43362.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>全球知名创意热店 Droga5 首席创意官 Ted Royer 遭到停职调查</b></a>，Droga5 拒绝描述本次调查的性质和原因。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cnad.com/show/12/288608.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>《中国广告》杂志统计了 2017 年年终各大广告公司新业务、业务流失的情况</b></a>，奥美凭借成都金融城项目、国际海事卫星组织项目、澳门购物节项目排名创意代理商第一位， 安索帕，电通排名第二三位， 盛世长城通过美林湖项目、沃尔玛项目、可口可乐项目等新业务上升至第八名。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：野兽派</p>"}